{"tid":691281,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【未賣先加價】北角柏蔚山狂加價15% 高一層賣貴「7球」","createTime":"2018-06-05T14:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T15:39:36.000Z","uid":68476,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74db5411a412f351d50fb8f9ee08ec72e32bf678","tid":691281,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"【未賣先加價】北角柏蔚山狂加價15% 高一層賣貴「7球」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180605/large/1528203029_9409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180605%2Flarge%2F1528203029_9409.jpg&h=04ff425b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新世界(017)北角柏蔚山未賣先加價，明天發售首批247伙之際，發展商突宣佈加推4號價單共100伙，部份單位狂加價15%。<br />\n<br />\n是次加推涉77伙三房戶及23伙四房戶，單位實用面積由808方呎至1,487方呎，部份單位提價15%，價單平均呎價38,552元，較上周推出的首張價單平均呎價35,041元貴約10%，訂價由2,741.6萬元至7,337.8萬元，呎價32,716元至高52,747元。扣除最高20%折扣後，折實平均呎價30,842元，折實價2,193.2萬至5,870.2萬元，呎價26,172元至42,197元。<br />\n<br />\n其中，4號價單售價最貴單位為1座30樓A室，實用面積1,487方呎，折實售價5,870.2萬元，呎價39,477元。與1號價單推出的1座29樓A室折實價5,104.56萬元及呎價34,328元比較，高一層賣貴15%或765.64萬元。"},{"pid":"128b35a3732399b73f3e0a45d0bba19301d86a28","tid":691281,"uid":28131,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b182f58cc9a1a71d642800acc06a74cc1d047ada","tid":691281,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"好扺買"},{"pid":"34a6ab3f6240dbd34bc210f1e9b1bda0907fda52","tid":691281,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:33:39.000Z","msg":"一層景觀貴七百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fc7793bcba479f0895dc5ac7aadb8387f0f573","tid":691281,"uid":68476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34a6ab3f6240dbd34bc210f1e9b1bda0907fda52","tid":691281,"uid":19552,